Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:02:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a "guiding light." The entrance to\Nthe Grand Line lies ahead of that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to find the All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become\Na master swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to draw a world map!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In order...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to become a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Precursor to a New Adventure!\NApis, a Mysterious Girl"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's meal time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?! Hey! Where're you?!\NWhere're you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's no use!\NIt's storming outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, you can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay put, we won't\Ndo anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, calm down!\N--What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search the whole ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her into custody\Nas soon as you find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still a child.\NDon't be rough on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's dangerous!\N--Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have the sail\Nunfurled like that in this storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect me, Grandpa Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! It's dangerous! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! What is this report?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl may be a clue to the Dragonite\Nthat I've spent years searching for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize how serious this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eric!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose a clue to the elixir of\Nimmortality after I've finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go join my fleet and find her\Nno matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tracking down someone\Nwasn't in the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you however much you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hired you for a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing a clue now will be a blow\Nfor you as well, will it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Your Excellency,\NCommodore Nelson Royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Aren't we in the Grand Line yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just left Loguetown two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a few more days.\NWait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nice weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That storm seems like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I see a flock of birds to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A flock of birds?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also see something\Nkind of big on the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it well.\NI wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Maybe a fish?\N--A small boat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a big fish, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I often hear that\Nseabirds flock above fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Let's have them for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Now that's a stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body sure is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a second...\NWhat're you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sorry, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna... cut him down... someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look. That's no fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is she a fishperson?\NWhere's her web?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. Just how does\Nshe look like a fishperson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was a little girl in\Na small boat like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you're doing\Nbetter than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.\NI'm cooking soup right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in a ship wreck or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've been in big trouble.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you ask someone questions,\Nyou should give your name first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good point. My name is Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's cooking soup\Nin the kitchen is Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with a scary face\Nwearing a bellyband is Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's unconscious\Nover there is Usopp. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy. I'm the captain\Nof this pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, well, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why? Why in the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through all that trouble and did\Nscary things to escape from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, why did I get\Npicked up by a pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll think about\Nit after I eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn no matter\Nhow many times I tell you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get it\Nthrough your thick skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask, I'll make something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, like I told you,\Ndon't take food without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Aren't you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't eat this afternoon, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you holding back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling ya, it's not\Npoisoned or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just sit there like that,\Nhe'll finish everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not eating, I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Sanji's the cook I picked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten anything this good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're finally smiling.\N--Oh, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating again, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't eat that much for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You emptied two pots, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got scared when you heard\Nwe're pirates, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a natural reaction\Ntowards pirates these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're not gonna sell me off?\N--No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all evil-looking, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a right\Nto talk with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have more, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, this ship isn't the kind\Nof pirate ship you're thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Another plate, please!\N--As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me, too!\N--Do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wo-oah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Just what'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was preparing a meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, breakfast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What breakfast explodes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You made this?\N--Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has quite... a unique appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'm digging in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to rescuing me,\Nyou're feeding me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything to help you from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be helpful... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop grumbling and just eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, is it really safe to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's possible that\Njust the appearance is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Was it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!\NI put in the wrong seasoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a common mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine if you\Nare careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she took the trouble\Nto prepare it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat every crumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't waste this\Ngirl's kindness. This girl's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's your name, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis! My name is Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis-chan put her heart into this food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I won't allow anyone to waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cook something\Nfor you later, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm not good at cooking...\Nbut I wanted to be helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.\NWe really appreciate the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the cooking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're many other things\Nthat you could help out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat barbecue next.\NI haven't had it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why were you\Ndrifting on the sea, Apis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I escaped from a Navy ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From a Navy ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...during the stormy\Nnight three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that small boat in such a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what'd you do in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means you weren't on\Ntheir ship as a guest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the Navy wouldn't\Ngo after every little villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you a super villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There's no way I'd do bad things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did bad things...\Nbut I can't tell you why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?\NShe must have her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't want to say,\Nthen we shouldn't press her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. But can you at\Nleast tell us where you're from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Warship Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it called Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the shape of the\Nisland looks exactly like a warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! This is the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's close to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're around here right now,\Nso it's not that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What do you wanna do?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna go\Nback to Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep sailing like this,\Nwe are going to enter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were nice enough to save me\Nand I feel bad burdening you further...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to go back to the island!\NI'm sorry. I'm selfish, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hand me to a ship heading\Nwest on your way if possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work things out on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, that's a real burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that a pirate ship can\Nget close to another ship so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since it's not totally out of our way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're not really in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, what the heck?\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter either way to me.\NWhat should we do, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line isn't\Nthat far, either, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The island looks\Nlike a warship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sounds like they've decided.\N--Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to stop\Nby Warship Island for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--All right! Thank you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show my appreciation,\NI'll prepare lots of dishes every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship sighted ahead at 13 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mid-size caravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a flag with a skull\Nmark on the main mast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know their own station,\Nsailing around in the seas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under Commodore Nelson's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're just small fries.\NJust leave them alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That flag doesn't\Nbelong to small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly,\Nthat belongs to Straw Hat Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man with a 30 million Berry\Nbounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the ones people have\Nbeen talking about lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still can't find the girl\Neven with this big fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that someone has her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, pirates of that caliber...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it going to be a problem if you\Nleave them be, Lt. Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this feeling is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I see ships\Napproaching from the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Ugh! Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're Navy ships!\N--Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just\None or two ships, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's a fleet like that doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they after my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot even for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that they need that\Nmany to capture me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so easygoing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those ships belong to Branch 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I escaped from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? There! I found her!\NI see the girl on their deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just as I said,\Nwasn't it, Lt. Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hurt your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you make a mistake\Nand lose that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the clue to the elixir\Nof immortality, the Dragonite,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how furious\NCommodore Nelson would get.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the main cannons!\NWe'll capture that pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! They're firing at us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention pirate ship!\NStop the ship immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were warning shots.\NThe next shots will hit your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'd stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do, Luffy? If you\Nwanna take 'em on, I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah. Why don't we?\N--Ahhh! W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys always like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the heck are you\Ngonna do against that fleet?!\N--Apis, go to the cabin downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll make a raid on them.\N--O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A raid isn't gonna work!\N--O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll make it work.\N--You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not saying you have to come.\NBack us up with the cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So I'm staying on this ship?\NOkay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And we'll get clear\Nof them at full speed!\N--Hey, Apis. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You take care of the rest.\N--Hey, Apis. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You take care of the rest.\N--He said a wind is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong wind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Lean the sail towards the south!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp and Sanji-kun,\Nright rudder full! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--O-Okay.\N--Yes, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gust is coming.\NWe'll ride it and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fight them head on,\Nwe'll lose no matter how good we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take them, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ship shows no signs of stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're mocking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! The pirate ship sped up\Nand changed its route!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--They're heading south!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,South?! How foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they know what's in that direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Lt. Commander?!\NGo after them! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is fast!\NThis is a good wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Luffy!\NThe Navy's falling behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You guys're slow turtles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! We can't catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Navy fleet falling behind\Nsuch a small ship? Dimwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A small ship has better mobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Commander, this ship will soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lt. Commander!\N--I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop all the ships!\NPrepare to turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lt. Commander!\NWhy are you stopping the ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep going,\Nwe'll go into the Calm Belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So what? Go after them!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't appreciate the\Nseriousness of this matter, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose that girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to say\Nto Commodore Nelson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to take the punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit by and let this fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my subordinates\Nbe swallowed by the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,\Nthe chase ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy isn't following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Captain Usopp\Nscare the pants off them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing! Just as\Nyou'd expect from our navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Nami-san. To think you\Ndetected such a wind beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was like an instinct, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami-san is lovely\Nwhen she's humble, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we head\Nstraight to Warship Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Really?!\N--Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! To Warship Island, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a serious look\Non your face for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hope it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this ship hasn't\Nbeen moving at all for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the sail\Nisn't catching any wind at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've entered the Calm Belt!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.31,0:24:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the Calm Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head straight to Warship Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always makes us do reckless things!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, don't you think Apis\Nhas an air of secrecy about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!\NSomething incredible's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.32,0:24:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.66,0:24:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode on One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.99,0:24:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miraculous Creature! Apis's Secret\Nand the Legendary Island."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.33,0:24:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.70,0:24:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
